n-upa.org.ua/gogun/dis_r02.html |archivedate=2013-03-21 }} ''See also:'' {{cite web |date=15 August 2011 |author=[[Grzegorz Rossoli\u0144ski-Liebe]] |location=University of Hamburg |publisher=Web journal 'Defending History' Vol. VII, No. 2458 |title=Article co-authored by Alexander Gogun, posted on the nationalist website \u2018OUN-UPA\u2019, obfuscates the Ukrainian Holocaust, denying OUN and UPA anti-Jewish Violence |url=http://defendinghistory.com/grzegorz-rossolinski-liebe-on-academic-article-that-obfuscates-the-holocaust-and-denies-oun-opa-anti-jewish-violence/20907 }}</ref> || Potsdam \n|-\n| Common communicate of PL and UKR historians || 50-60k || 20-25k || \u2013 || ||5-6k || \"Polska-Ukraina: trudne pytania\", 2000, t. 9, p.&nbsp;403. || \"Polish casualties acc. to Polish sources\" \n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:left; background:#d0e7ff;\"| Ryszard Torzecki || 30-40k || 30-40k|| || 80-100k || 10-20k (Polesie and Lublin)|| R. Torzecki, ''Polacy i Ukrai\u0144cy. Sprawa ukrai\u0144ska podczas II wojny \u015bwiatowej na terenie II Rzeczypospolitej'', 1993, p.&nbsp;267 ||\n|- \n| [[Institute of National Remembrance|IPN]] || 60-80k ||  \u2013  || \u2013 || \u2013 || || [https://web.archive.org/web/20111210220312/http://ipn.gov.pl/portal/pl/833/14484/Sledztwa_w_biegu.html Oddzia\u0142owa Komisja w Lublinie, January 2012]||killed by Ukrainian nationalists, 1939\u20131945? \n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:left; background:#d0e7ff;\"| Norman Davies|| \u2013 ||  \u2013  ||- || hundreds of thousands|| || 'God's playground. A history of Poland', Oxford University Press, 2005, p.&nbsp;350 || ethnic cleansing\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:left; background:#d0e7ff;\"| Czes\u0142aw Partacz|| \u2013 || \u2013 || \u2013 || 134-200k || || ''Przemilczane w ukrai\u0144skiej historiografii przyczyny ludob\u00f3jstwa pope\u0142nionego przez OUN-UPA na ludno\u015bci polskiej'' [in:] ''Prawda historyczna na prawda polityczna w badaniach naukowych. Przyk\u0142ad ludob\u00f3jstwa na Kresach Po\u